snippet.textDisplay: Art student here! You can dye cotton with lots of different foods. Avocado works if you boil a bunch of peels and pits at once then add the shirt afterwards, you may also need a mordant. It might not be hot pink (when I did it, it was more of an orange). It might depend on the quality of avocado though if that makes sense 😂 you can also use wine, blueberries, turmeric...
